<h2 id="1-1-세-정수의-최대값-구하기">1-1. 세 정수의 최대값 구하기</h2>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">'세 정수의 최대값을 구하라.'</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">a</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">int</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">input</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">'정수 a 값 입력: '</span><span class="p">))</span>
<span class="n">b</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">int</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">input</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">'정수 b 값 입력: '</span><span class="p">))</span>
<span class="n">c</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">int</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">input</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">'정수 c 값 입력: '</span><span class="p">))</span>

<span class="n">maximum</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">a</span>
<span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">b</span> <span class="o">&gt;</span> <span class="n">maximum</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="n">maximum</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">b</span>
<span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">c</span> <span class="o">&gt;</span> <span class="n">maximum</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="n">maximum</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">c</span>
</code></pre></div></div>
